title: Allman Brothers - 2005-08-14 - Rosemont Theater in Rosemont, IL
description:
Allman Brothers Band
2005-08-14
DTE Energy Music Theatre
Clarkston, MI


Sister show to 08/13/05 with Jack Pearson subbing all night for Warren Haynes. Highlights include slide on Stateboro and Dreams plus incredible 
straight ahead solo on Mountain Jam. Nice throwback intro to You Don't Love Me also.
